    <item>
      <title>Music Morons Weed</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/posts/music-morons-weed/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 20:22:50 -0400</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/posts/music-morons-weed/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;rumblecom-video&#34;&gt;Rumble.com Video&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;script&gt;!function(r,u,m,b,l,e){r._Rumble=b,r[b]||(r[b]=function(){(r[b]._=r[b]._||[]).push(arguments);if(r[b]._.length==1){l=u.createElement(m),e=u.getElementsByTagName(m)[0],l.async=1,l.src=&#34;https://rumble.com/embedJS/u17ojy5&#34;+(arguments[1].video?&#39;.&#39;+arguments[1].video:&#39;&#39;)+&#34;/?url=&#34;+encodeURIComponent(location.href)+&#34;&amp;args=&#34;+encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify([].slice.apply(arguments))),e.parentNode.insertBefore(l,e)}})}(window, document, &#34;script&#34;, &#34;Rumble&#34;);&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;rumble_v48khml&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;script&gt;&#xA;Rumble(&#34;play&#34;, {&#34;video&#34;:&#34;v48khml&#34;,&#34;div&#34;:&#34;rumble_v48khml&#34;});&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;click-here-to-play-this-video-on-torhttpcastgardn7yj746n7nyt3udot5orhpqfs36sl7rq2y3yd4su6ruuddydonionwcnz9urimhu9sknyec3vtds&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://castgardn7yj746n7nyt3udot5orhpqfs36sl7rq2y3yd4su6ruuddyd.onion/w/cnZ9uRimHU9SKnYEc3vTdS&#34;&gt;Click here to play this video on Tor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Tonight John &amp;amp; I went over a little about our histories and back stories. Then we moved into talking more about our former band and even play a special unreleased song from their EP thats in production. Then the conversation took a drastic turn into the world of weed and a cool little mobile app to help you find it, legally. Check the laws where you live. Weed may not be legal for you. Luckily for us, it is where we are.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
